      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Unconscious]{Unconscious} conditions from filth fever don't improve on their own until the disease is cured.</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:fortitude|dc:14]</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> carrier with no ill effect (1d4 hours),</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1} (1 day),</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 1} (1 day),</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Unconscious]{Unconscious} (1 day),</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 5</strong> dead</p>"
        },
